只有國殤 】遊行<br />\n2019年10月1日<br />\n下午兩時起步<br />\n維園集合，遊行往遮打道<br />\n<br />\n主辦︰民間人權陣線<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A8Dkz2M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA8Dkz2M.jpg&h=c7d62bd7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qS9jQCv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqS9jQCv.jpg&h=769335de&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hqy41Ka.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHqy41Ka.jpg&h=a6dbaf1c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WJQZQCw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWJQZQCw.jpg&h=ba39fbf6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YBnxrpS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYBnxrpS.jpg&h=5d06ca10&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c29d963037e854b173553ff5eea30651abe0a544","tid":1579671,"uid":266672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T12:28:58.000Z","msg":"搞元氣同starbucks先"}]}